Module scenebuilder.core
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.api.util

Class SceneBuilderBeanFactory.DocumentScope

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.api.util.SceneBuilderBeanFactory.DocumentScope
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.beans.factory.config.Scope
Enclosing class:
SceneBuilderBeanFactory
public static class SceneBuilderBeanFactory.DocumentScope
extends Object
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.config.Scope
The Class DocumentScope is a Spring scope. The scoped document change when a new Document window is instantiated The scoped document change when a Document window gain focus The document scope is removed when a Document window is closed
